WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:07.868 --> 00:01:09.369 line:80%
[♪ inspiring music playing]

00:01:22.007 --> 00:01:23.008 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:01:24.467 --> 00:01:25.635 line:80%
Come on out now.

00:01:42.277 --> 00:01:43.361 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:01:44.029 --> 00:01:46.239 line:80%
-Just give me a second!
-[music stops abruptly]

00:01:46.740 --> 00:01:49.367 line:80%
Don't you find him to be so impatient?

00:01:49.451 --> 00:01:52.245 line:80%
Ah. He is generally of
a most easygoing disposition. [chuckles]

00:01:52.329 --> 00:01:53.705 line:80%
[I-AN] We're late!

00:01:53.788 --> 00:01:55.832 line:80%
-Why that…
-No, Your Ladyship! [chuckles]

00:01:57.876 --> 00:01:59.252 line:80%
[sighs] My apologies.

00:02:02.130 --> 00:02:03.715 line:80%
Yes, please check the seat number for me.

00:02:03.798 --> 00:02:04.799 line:80%
-Thank you.
-[sighs]

00:02:06.801 --> 00:02:09.429 line:80%
Wait, is Ms. Seong still getting dressed?

00:02:09.512 --> 00:02:11.097 line:80%
She must be sewing the gown herself.

00:02:11.598 --> 00:02:13.600 line:80%
She could've made two by now.

00:02:14.392 --> 00:02:15.393 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:02:18.104 --> 00:02:19.814 line:80%
Well, at this rate…

00:02:19.898 --> 00:02:21.441 line:80%
[♪ dreamy music playing]

00:02:25.695 --> 00:02:28.823 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:02:29.616 --> 00:02:30.700 line:20%
EPISODE 6

00:02:30.784 --> 00:02:34.704 line:20%
Her Majesty said your attendance
would not be required.

00:02:34.788 --> 00:02:37.207 line:20%
Uncle insisted I be there.

00:02:37.999 --> 00:02:39.167 line:20%
His Royal Highness did?

00:02:39.751 --> 00:02:40.752 line:20%
Yes.

00:02:45.173 --> 00:02:46.174 line:20%
[crickets chirping]

00:02:46.967 --> 00:02:48.009 line:20%
[exhales sharply]

00:02:53.264 --> 00:02:54.265 line:20%
Your Majesty.

00:02:58.019 --> 00:02:59.104 line:80%
You came.

00:02:59.187 --> 00:03:02.691 line:80%
How could I refuse a request
from the Queen Mother?

00:03:11.199 --> 00:03:13.243 line:80%
[♪ classical dance music playing]

00:03:22.794 --> 00:03:25.422 line:80%
Announcing Her Majesty the Queen Mother.

00:03:25.505 --> 00:03:27.090 line:80%
[♪ string ensemble stops playing]

00:04:05.295 --> 00:04:07.756 line:80%
Thank you for inviting me, Your Majesty.

00:04:08.715 --> 00:04:11.926 line:80%
I would've been most delighted
to have been invited to the reception too.

00:04:12.010 --> 00:04:13.219 line:80%
It is such a shame…

00:04:16.890 --> 00:04:18.224 line:80%
[stammers]

00:04:18.308 --> 00:04:19.893 line:80%
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:04:22.979 --> 00:04:24.939 line:80%
I hope you enjoy the banquet.

00:04:33.948 --> 00:04:36.367 line:80%
How would you find her
as Grand Prince I-AN's consort?

00:04:42.999 --> 00:04:45.668 line:80%
She is neither too remarkable
nor of too humble a station.

00:04:46.503 --> 00:04:48.088 line:80%
Is she not quite suitable?

00:04:50.215 --> 00:04:52.258 line:80%
[attendant] Announcing Grand Prince I-AN.

00:04:56.596 --> 00:04:58.098 line:80%
[♪ dreamy music playing]

00:05:45.895 --> 00:05:47.063 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:05:53.194 --> 00:05:55.196 line:80%
[♪ string ensemble resumes playing]

00:06:40.074 --> 00:06:41.910 line:80%
It was a request from I-AN.

00:06:44.537 --> 00:06:47.415 line:80%
It seems he wishes to leave her
a handsome parting gift.

00:06:50.251 --> 00:06:51.461 line:80%
We must honor his wishes.

00:06:55.340 --> 00:06:57.342 line:80%
So there is a use for this after all.

00:06:58.051 --> 00:06:59.469 line:80%
[Huiju] Don't you dance this often?

00:07:00.261 --> 00:07:02.013 line:80%
I hated these lessons the most.

00:07:02.597 --> 00:07:03.598 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:07:04.307 --> 00:07:05.308 line:80%
[whispers] Me too.

00:07:05.850 --> 00:07:06.851 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:07:15.235 --> 00:07:16.611 line:80%
[guests murmuring]

00:07:24.494 --> 00:07:25.703 line:80%
Even so,

00:07:26.287 --> 00:07:27.622 line:80%
this seems quite effective.

00:07:28.623 --> 00:07:29.832 line:80%
Everyone's eyes are on us.

00:07:42.387 --> 00:07:43.805 line:80%
You should only have eyes for me.

00:07:45.306 --> 00:07:47.809 line:80%
As if we were hopelessly in love.

00:07:50.436 --> 00:07:53.189 line:80%
I hear you, but this won't be enough.

00:07:53.273 --> 00:07:54.399 line:80%
I know.

00:08:06.452 --> 00:08:08.162 line:80%
-[♪ music ends]
-[applauding]

00:08:20.174 --> 00:08:21.301 line:80%
Follow my lead.

00:08:28.891 --> 00:08:30.643 line:80%
[guests gasping, whispering]

00:08:41.279 --> 00:08:43.197 line:80%
[guest 1] Wait,
don't tell me that ring is…

00:08:43.281 --> 00:08:44.866 line:80%
[guest 2] Is that Queen UIHYEON's ring?

00:08:45.742 --> 00:08:47.452 line:80%
[guest 3] Gosh, she's so lucky.

00:08:49.495 --> 00:08:50.913 line:80%
[whispers] Your Royal Highness.

00:08:53.333 --> 00:08:54.709 line:80%
Compared to you…

00:08:56.836 --> 00:08:58.504 line:80%
my pace may seem much slower.

00:09:01.466 --> 00:09:02.592 line:80%
Even so…

00:09:05.928 --> 00:09:07.638 line:80%
will you give me your hand in marriage?

00:09:07.722 --> 00:09:09.140 line:80%
[guests chattering]

00:09:11.934 --> 00:09:13.144 line:80%
[♪ joyful music playing]

00:09:19.484 --> 00:09:22.195 line:80%
-[guests applauding]
-[fireworks exploding]

00:10:26.384 --> 00:10:27.385 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:10:29.178 --> 00:10:30.221 line:80%
Will you honor us

00:10:31.389 --> 00:10:32.640 line:80%
with your royal blessing?

00:10:33.891 --> 00:10:34.892 line:80%
[exhales deeply]

00:10:34.976 --> 00:10:36.227 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:10:42.066 --> 00:10:43.401 line:80%
[♪ music stops]

00:10:45.111 --> 00:10:46.112 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:10:55.705 --> 00:10:57.081 line:80%
You have my blessing.

00:10:57.957 --> 00:10:59.667 line:80%
[♪ joyful music resumes]

00:11:03.463 --> 00:11:05.465 line:80%
I wish you great happiness, Uncle.

00:11:06.257 --> 00:11:07.467 line:80%
You too, Ms. Seong.

00:11:08.176 --> 00:11:09.260 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:11:10.970 --> 00:11:13.264 line:80%
I am deeply honored, Your Majesty.

00:11:14.432 --> 00:11:15.641 line:80%
[guests cheering]

00:11:39.165 --> 00:11:40.166 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:11:40.666 --> 00:11:41.667 line:80%
[owl hoots]

00:11:46.714 --> 00:11:47.882 line:80%
[breathing heavily]

00:11:52.386 --> 00:11:53.429 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:12:01.103 --> 00:12:02.438 line:80%
Utilize your veto power.

00:12:02.522 --> 00:12:03.940 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:12:04.023 --> 00:12:06.400 line:80%
Royal marriages must be approved
by the prime minister.

00:12:06.484 --> 00:12:08.945 line:80%
His Majesty approved it
with everyone watching.

00:12:09.028 --> 00:12:10.321 line:80%
That is exactly why!

00:12:13.533 --> 00:12:15.368 line:80%
You are the only option we have.

00:12:24.627 --> 00:12:26.420 line:80%
The Crown and the Cabinet

00:12:27.880 --> 00:12:29.173 line:80%
must remain unified.

00:12:41.561 --> 00:12:42.603 line:80%
[exhales deeply]

00:12:44.480 --> 00:12:45.523 line:80%
That's right.

00:12:45.606 --> 00:12:47.817 line:80%
Yes, of course. All right, then.

00:12:50.444 --> 00:12:52.238 line:80%
You must've had quite a day.

00:12:52.738 --> 00:12:54.532 line:80%
Oh. Aide Choi.

00:12:54.615 --> 00:12:56.576 line:80%
Is there usually no cell service here?

00:12:56.659 --> 00:12:59.745 line:80%
Ah. They probably blocked the signal today
because of all the guests.

00:12:59.829 --> 00:13:02.623 line:80%
Ah. Then is there anywhere
with a wired connection?

00:13:02.707 --> 00:13:03.916 line:80%
Wired connection…

00:13:04.709 --> 00:13:05.710 line:80%
Follow me.

00:13:12.842 --> 00:13:15.469 line:80%
Our sincerest congratulations,
Your Royal Highness.

00:13:17.096 --> 00:13:18.306 line:80%
To you as well, Ms. Seong.

00:13:22.059 --> 00:13:23.060 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

00:14:05.019 --> 00:14:06.020 line:80%
Who knew

00:14:06.729 --> 00:14:08.814 line:80%
you had such a gift for deception?

00:14:09.982 --> 00:14:12.401 line:80%
I meant what I said when we spoke earlier.

00:14:13.694 --> 00:14:15.112 line:80%
Though you may not believe me.

00:14:16.656 --> 00:14:18.532 line:80%
Did you think
I would simply let this stand?

00:14:20.534 --> 00:14:21.911 line:80%
And if you do not?

00:14:23.954 --> 00:14:26.999 line:80%
Do you plan to go against
His Majesty's royal command?

00:14:40.137 --> 00:14:41.597 line:80%
Do not be too enraged.

00:14:43.391 --> 00:14:45.017 line:80%
I simply wanted my marriage

00:14:46.143 --> 00:14:47.895 line:80%
to be conducted on my terms.

00:14:49.647 --> 00:14:51.982 line:80%
A grand prince's marriage is hardly
a private matter.

00:14:52.733 --> 00:14:54.318 line:80%
How did someone so well-informed…

00:14:57.071 --> 00:14:58.239 line:80%
ever see fit

00:14:59.573 --> 00:15:00.866 line:80%
to amend my brother's will?

00:15:14.547 --> 00:15:16.048 line:80%
-That is absurd--
-Smile.

00:15:18.008 --> 00:15:19.635 line:80%
There are many eyes on us.

00:15:33.190 --> 00:15:34.191 line:80%
[Huiju] Jeongwoo.

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:37.361 line:80%
Shall we?

00:15:51.834 --> 00:15:53.461 line:80%
That ruthless brat never showed up?

00:15:53.544 --> 00:15:55.713 line:80%
Yeah, she's not in her room
or the library either.

00:15:55.796 --> 00:15:57.923 line:80%
I thought the ninth graders
had their exam today.

00:15:58.007 --> 00:16:00.342 line:80%
I guess she won't be
the top laureate this time.

00:16:00.426 --> 00:16:01.719 line:80%
Maybe someone locked her up.

00:16:01.802 --> 00:16:03.804 line:80%
[student 1] You think?
But who would do that?

00:16:03.888 --> 00:16:05.139 line:80%
[student 2] You never know.

00:16:05.222 --> 00:16:06.932 line:80%
She was always early, though.

00:16:12.855 --> 00:16:15.566 line:80%
ELEVATOR OUT OF ORDER

00:16:15.649 --> 00:16:17.276 line:80%
-[panting]
-[pounding on door]

00:16:17.359 --> 00:16:18.360 line:80%
[young Huiju] Hello?

00:16:19.153 --> 00:16:20.988 line:80%
Is anyone out there?

00:16:21.572 --> 00:16:22.823 line:80%
Hello?

00:16:23.365 --> 00:16:24.450 line:80%
Damn it!

00:16:26.994 --> 00:16:28.829 line:80%
-There's someone in here!
-Huiju?

00:16:30.164 --> 00:16:31.332 line:80%
[grunts]

00:16:33.042 --> 00:16:34.043 line:80%
Jeongwoo.

00:16:34.543 --> 00:16:36.921 line:80%
[breathes heavily] Take my hand.

00:16:39.256 --> 00:16:40.674 line:80%
[both grunt]

00:16:42.676 --> 00:16:44.094 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:16:44.178 --> 00:16:46.263 line:80%
[gasps] Come with me.

00:16:48.599 --> 00:16:49.767 line:80%
Where are we going?

00:16:49.850 --> 00:16:52.144 line:80%
-You tell them for me.
-What?

00:16:52.228 --> 00:16:55.314 line:80%
Tell them I'm late
because I was trapped in there.

00:16:56.190 --> 00:16:57.858 line:80%
They'll believe you.

00:16:57.942 --> 00:16:59.318 line:80%
[♪ dreamy music playing]

00:17:36.438 --> 00:17:38.023 line:80%
Are you still against this marriage?

00:17:41.235 --> 00:17:42.444 line:80%
Can't you give me a break?

00:17:43.445 --> 00:17:46.115 line:80%
If I lose you, I'll have no one left.

00:18:27.072 --> 00:18:28.115 line:80%
Promise me.

00:18:29.199 --> 00:18:30.826 line:80%
That you'll never lie to me again.

00:18:33.203 --> 00:18:35.831 line:80%
Then I'll always be on your side.

00:18:43.380 --> 00:18:44.381 line:80%
Okay.

00:18:45.424 --> 00:18:46.425 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:19:00.606 --> 00:19:01.607 line:80%
[Huiju sighs]

00:19:03.359 --> 00:19:04.401 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:19:05.694 --> 00:19:07.196 line:80%
This is Queen UIHYEON's ring, right?

00:19:08.405 --> 00:19:10.157 line:80%
She always wore it.

00:19:11.033 --> 00:19:13.452 line:80%
I saw it when I was a kid,
but I still remember it.

00:19:14.078 --> 00:19:15.287 line:80%
It was just so pretty.

00:19:18.165 --> 00:19:20.960 line:80%
But are you sure
you can just give this to me?

00:19:21.460 --> 00:19:22.670 line:80%
It's your mother's ring.

00:19:24.254 --> 00:19:25.464 line:80%
Of course not.

00:19:26.090 --> 00:19:27.758 line:80%
That is a national treasure.

00:19:27.841 --> 00:19:29.218 line:80%
Return it when we get divorced.

00:19:31.011 --> 00:19:32.346 line:80%
Geez, just take it now.

00:19:32.429 --> 00:19:34.264 line:80%
They've already got plenty of shots of it.

00:19:34.348 --> 00:19:35.641 line:80%
Forget it.

00:19:36.767 --> 00:19:38.769 line:80%
Mother didn't even like that ring.

00:19:39.603 --> 00:19:40.604 line:80%
Why not?

00:19:42.439 --> 00:19:43.691 line:80%
Perhaps it was too heavy?

00:19:56.996 --> 00:19:59.248 line:80%
I guess you were her favorite.

00:20:00.916 --> 00:20:03.335 line:80%
This ring is
a national treasure, after all.

00:20:04.294 --> 00:20:05.963 line:80%
Yet she passed it down to you.

00:20:06.046 --> 00:20:08.215 line:80%
Not to your brother, the future king.

00:20:13.679 --> 00:20:14.680 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:20:17.474 --> 00:20:19.977 line:80%
That decision left my father furious.

00:20:22.312 --> 00:20:23.355 line:80%
Father…

00:20:24.940 --> 00:20:26.483 line:80%
detested giving me anything.

00:20:30.571 --> 00:20:31.697 line:80%
[sighs]

00:20:40.622 --> 00:20:41.749 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

00:20:41.832 --> 00:20:42.958 line:80%
That's fathers for you.

00:20:48.380 --> 00:20:49.423 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:20:50.507 --> 00:20:51.759 line:80%
[breathes deeply]

00:20:55.804 --> 00:20:57.222 line:80%
[♪ romantic music playing]

00:21:56.865 --> 00:21:58.075 line:80%
[Hyeon] My goodness.

00:21:59.034 --> 00:22:00.911 line:80%
Could you be any prettier?

00:22:00.994 --> 00:22:02.329 line:80%
Do you like roses?

00:22:03.288 --> 00:22:04.289 line:80%
Pardon?

00:22:04.373 --> 00:22:06.166 line:80%
David Austin. Juliet roses.

00:22:06.250 --> 00:22:07.876 line:80%
These are Peony roses.

00:22:07.960 --> 00:22:10.003 line:80%
-They're all roses.
-Huh?

00:22:10.087 --> 00:22:11.880 line:80%
My parents run a flower shop.

00:22:14.341 --> 00:22:15.342 line:80%
Ms. Do,

00:22:15.425 --> 00:22:17.886 line:80%
-are you a flower shop heiress?
-[door opens]

00:22:18.554 --> 00:22:19.680 line:80%
How's the response been?

00:22:20.848 --> 00:22:22.933 line:80%
They're going nuts out there.

00:22:23.559 --> 00:22:25.602 line:80%
Because of the proposal?
Did foreign media pick it up?

00:22:25.686 --> 00:22:29.273 line:80%
-Both domestic and international media.
-Ha. [giggles]

00:22:29.356 --> 00:22:31.400 line:80%
KOREAN PRINCE'S PROPOSAL
BREAKS CLASS BARRIER

00:22:31.483 --> 00:22:32.901 line:80%
I-AN PROPOSES TO SEONG HUIJU

00:22:34.403 --> 00:22:35.404 line:80%
[sighs deeply]

00:22:36.238 --> 00:22:38.073 line:80%
Set up a meeting
with the PR team tomorrow.

00:22:38.657 --> 00:22:40.159 line:80%
I already set it all up.

00:22:40.242 --> 00:22:41.952 line:80%
It's at 10:00 a.m. tomorrow.

00:22:44.037 --> 00:22:47.666 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, can I wear this ring
to my interview tomorrow?

00:22:50.043 --> 00:22:51.962 line:80%
-Do as you wish.
-[giggles]

00:22:52.921 --> 00:22:54.840 line:80%
Look at it. Isn't it so pretty?

00:22:54.923 --> 00:22:57.426 line:80%
-[softly] It's so pretty.
-Look with your eyes, not your hands.

00:22:59.970 --> 00:23:00.971 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:23:04.099 --> 00:23:05.100 line:80%
So pretty.

00:23:06.560 --> 00:23:08.103 line:80%
Wow, this is insane.

00:23:08.187 --> 00:23:09.855 line:80%
He proposed to her?

00:23:10.856 --> 00:23:13.942 line:80%
Babe, we're officially a royal family now!

00:23:14.026 --> 00:23:15.611 line:80%
I know, right?

00:23:15.694 --> 00:23:18.030 line:80%
So I'm officially Grand Prince I-AN's…

00:23:20.199 --> 00:23:21.366 line:80%
brother-in-law now.

00:23:21.450 --> 00:23:22.701 line:80%
That's right.

00:23:33.253 --> 00:23:34.254 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:23:36.882 --> 00:23:38.383 line:80%
Something doesn't feel right.

00:23:38.467 --> 00:23:42.346 line:80%
You just don't like the idea
of Huiju becoming a royal, do you?

00:23:42.429 --> 00:23:45.015 line:80%
No, that's not it.

00:23:45.098 --> 00:23:47.392 line:80%
Babe, she needs to become a royal

00:23:47.476 --> 00:23:49.978 line:80%
for you to become
the sole Castle Group heir.

00:23:50.771 --> 00:23:52.189 line:80%
I know that.

00:23:52.981 --> 00:23:54.107 line:80%
-Then what?
-[stammers]

00:23:56.944 --> 00:23:58.987 line:80%
About that damn mechanic who died.

00:23:59.071 --> 00:24:00.781 line:80%
Don't you think something feels off?

00:24:03.742 --> 00:24:06.495 line:80%
[sucks teeth] You have a point.

00:24:08.789 --> 00:24:09.873 line:80%
[sighs]

00:24:20.300 --> 00:24:21.551 line:80%
Announce me.

00:24:21.635 --> 00:24:22.761 line:80%
[Im] Your Majesty.

00:24:23.637 --> 00:24:25.555 line:80%
Lord INPYEONG has arrived.

00:24:26.473 --> 00:24:27.599 line:80%
Show him in.

00:24:41.530 --> 00:24:42.823 line:80%
Nuptials?

00:24:43.615 --> 00:24:44.783 line:80%
This is nonsense.

00:24:46.827 --> 00:24:49.121 line:80%
I will petition His Majesty
to rescind his command.

00:24:49.204 --> 00:24:50.247 line:80%
You will do no such thing.

00:24:51.415 --> 00:24:54.042 line:80%
A royal command that can be overturned
in the blink of an eye

00:24:55.585 --> 00:24:57.004 line:80%
is no command at all.

00:24:57.587 --> 00:24:58.588 line:80%
So?

00:24:59.423 --> 00:25:01.258 line:80%
Will you just accept it?

00:25:05.220 --> 00:25:06.430 line:80%
Grand Prince I-AN…

00:25:08.890 --> 00:25:10.851 line:80%
knows about the late King's dying wish.

00:25:14.855 --> 00:25:17.316 line:80%
You intend for Grand Prince I-AN
to ascend the throne?

00:25:18.358 --> 00:25:20.652 line:80%
Have you truly gone mad?

00:25:22.070 --> 00:25:23.905 line:80%
It will be better than dying.

00:25:28.243 --> 00:25:30.037 line:80%
It would be better to die.

00:25:34.791 --> 00:25:36.335 line:80%
I'd rather see you dead.

00:25:38.170 --> 00:25:39.338 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:25:46.053 --> 00:25:48.055 line:80%
For the sake of the Crown Prince.

00:25:53.935 --> 00:25:56.355 line:80%
It did not appear to be
a remark made in passing.

00:25:57.731 --> 00:26:00.150 line:80%
-You were certain--
-I doubt he has any evidence.

00:26:04.237 --> 00:26:05.364 line:80%
<i>The fire that day…</i>

00:26:10.869 --> 00:26:12.579 line:80%
<i>reduced everything to ashes.</i>

00:26:15.248 --> 00:26:16.249 line:80%
Thus,

00:26:16.333 --> 00:26:18.251 line:80%
I shall accept

00:26:18.335 --> 00:26:19.878 line:80%
that unsavory union.

00:26:21.338 --> 00:26:24.049 line:80%
-Your Majesty.
-As long as he knows about that will,

00:26:24.591 --> 00:26:26.593 line:80%
we can never join forces with him.

00:26:26.676 --> 00:26:28.470 line:80%
-So?
-Seong Huiju.

00:26:30.472 --> 00:26:32.391 line:80%
She will prove to be his weakness.

00:26:34.017 --> 00:26:36.269 line:80%
It would be best to keep her
within arm's reach.

00:26:37.354 --> 00:26:39.189 line:80%
Do you not agree?

00:26:49.157 --> 00:26:52.244 line:80%
A 21ST CENTURY CINDERELLA,
COMMONER TO ROYALTY

00:26:56.915 --> 00:26:59.668 line:80%
I'm not entirely on board either,
but what choice do we have?

00:26:59.751 --> 00:27:01.378 line:80%
He's right, Father.

00:27:01.461 --> 00:27:04.381 line:80%
There was a public proposal,
and His Majesty gave them his blessing.

00:27:06.591 --> 00:27:07.884 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:27:07.968 --> 00:27:11.179 line:80%
Father, maybe we can take this chance
to redistribute the company shares--

00:27:11.263 --> 00:27:12.722 line:80%
Dayeong.

00:27:13.223 --> 00:27:14.349 line:80%
Yes?

00:27:15.392 --> 00:27:16.893 line:80%
I need you to call your parents.

00:27:17.477 --> 00:27:19.104 line:80%
[stutters] My parents?

00:27:19.896 --> 00:27:22.274 line:80%
We need to plant someone in the palace.

00:27:25.318 --> 00:27:26.653 line:80%
Your sister

00:27:27.612 --> 00:27:30.323 line:80%
should have at least one person
she can rely on.

00:27:32.576 --> 00:27:37.664 line:20%
CASTLE BEAUTY

00:27:50.177 --> 00:27:51.720 line:80%
-By the way, Babe.
-Yes?

00:27:51.803 --> 00:27:54.264 line:80%
I thought your father disliked Huiju.

00:27:55.140 --> 00:27:58.059 line:80%
He does dislike her, but he hates it more
when others pick on her.

00:27:58.685 --> 00:27:59.686 line:80%
What?

00:28:00.228 --> 00:28:01.646 line:80%
That's just how he is.

00:28:01.730 --> 00:28:02.898 line:80%
[gasps]

00:28:05.525 --> 00:28:07.319 line:80%
I can't believe I'm seeing it in person.

00:28:08.361 --> 00:28:09.613 line:80%
How many carats is this?

00:28:11.114 --> 00:28:12.866 line:80%
-Seriously? [clicks tongue]
-[grunts]

00:28:14.242 --> 00:28:15.285 line:80%
Well, anyway…

00:28:16.119 --> 00:28:18.497 line:80%
Have you named your successor yet?

00:28:20.123 --> 00:28:21.124 line:80%
My successor?

00:28:21.208 --> 00:28:22.709 line:80%
Royals can't work.

00:28:22.792 --> 00:28:25.378 line:80%
Then, you know, your company…

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:29.174 line:80%
You'll need to hand over
your management rights.

00:28:31.009 --> 00:28:33.094 line:80%
-So?
-What do you mean, "So"?

00:28:33.595 --> 00:28:34.804 line:80%
I mean…

00:28:35.514 --> 00:28:37.557 line:80%
This company is your life's work.

00:28:37.641 --> 00:28:39.309 line:80%
This is when family steps up.

00:28:40.060 --> 00:28:43.605 line:80%
You wouldn't want to hand it over
to a complete stranger…

00:28:44.189 --> 00:28:45.315 line:80%
Right?

00:28:45.398 --> 00:28:47.859 line:80%
-Don't you agree, babe?
-Of course. Yes.

00:28:48.360 --> 00:28:50.487 line:80%
Your dear brother will take good--

00:28:50.570 --> 00:28:53.615 line:80%
That is my decision to make.

00:28:54.199 --> 00:28:57.285 line:80%
Did you find out what I asked about?

00:28:58.078 --> 00:29:00.121 line:80%
Talking to you is like
talking to a brick wall.

00:29:01.790 --> 00:29:03.500 line:80%
[sighs] Anyway… [clears throat]

00:29:04.209 --> 00:29:05.460 line:80%
…I did find him.

00:29:05.544 --> 00:29:08.547 line:80%
He went to great lengths to find him.

00:29:08.630 --> 00:29:09.965 line:80%
[Taeju] I know, right?

00:29:10.048 --> 00:29:12.467 line:80%
Listen, it was not easy at all. Nowadays…

00:29:12.551 --> 00:29:13.677 line:80%
Damn it.

00:29:15.345 --> 00:29:16.596 line:80%
She just won't let me talk.

00:29:18.557 --> 00:29:19.558 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:29:20.308 --> 00:29:21.351 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:29:23.979 --> 00:29:25.021 line:80%
He's dead.

00:29:27.857 --> 00:29:28.984 line:80%
What?

00:29:29.067 --> 00:29:30.193 line:80%
He died.

00:29:30.277 --> 00:29:32.862 line:80%
So I dug around a little, just in case,

00:29:32.946 --> 00:29:34.239 line:80%
but I found nothing.

00:29:34.990 --> 00:29:36.616 line:80%
No parents. No siblings.

00:29:42.414 --> 00:29:43.582 line:80%
[exhales sharply]

00:29:49.963 --> 00:29:53.758 line:80%
Listen, you meet all kinds
of crazy people in life.

00:29:53.842 --> 00:29:56.720 line:80%
-For… [bleep] …sake!
-Damn, you scared me.

00:29:57.971 --> 00:30:00.932 line:80%
That… [bleep]
…I should've killed him myself.

00:30:01.016 --> 00:30:02.726 line:80%
But some… [bleep] …asshole beat me to it!

00:30:04.019 --> 00:30:06.479 line:80%
I forgot who you were for a second there.

00:30:06.563 --> 00:30:07.981 line:80%
[knock on door]

00:30:08.064 --> 00:30:09.149 line:80%
[grunting]

00:30:10.442 --> 00:30:12.736 line:80%
That's five minutes.
You need to leave now.

00:30:12.819 --> 00:30:14.446 line:80%
-Us?
-Yes.

00:30:14.529 --> 00:30:17.824 line:80%
Wow, our company nowadays is just…
Nobody knows their place anymore.

00:30:17.907 --> 00:30:19.075 line:80%
-Let's go.
-Okay.

00:30:21.411 --> 00:30:22.412 line:80%
Never again.

00:30:23.913 --> 00:30:26.583 line:80%
Telling me to leave?
I'm a Senior Managing Director, you know.

00:30:26.666 --> 00:30:27.834 line:80%
My apologies.

00:30:27.917 --> 00:30:28.918 line:80%
Take care.

00:30:31.880 --> 00:30:32.964 line:80%
[exhales deeply]

00:30:41.640 --> 00:30:44.309 line:80%
This is the list of anticipated questions.
Take a look.

00:30:44.392 --> 00:30:45.393 line:80%
Okay.

00:30:47.729 --> 00:30:48.730 line:80%
[sighs]

00:30:49.814 --> 00:30:53.151 line:80%
Why are these questions so cliché?

00:30:53.234 --> 00:30:55.904 line:80%
"The Grand Prince's strengths
and weaknesses?"

00:30:56.446 --> 00:30:57.989 line:80%
Who would even care?

00:30:58.698 --> 00:31:00.158 line:80%
It should be more like…

00:31:00.241 --> 00:31:01.660 line:80%
"When was your first kiss?"

00:31:01.743 --> 00:31:03.787 line:80%
"Who wins in a fight behind closed doors?"

00:31:03.870 --> 00:31:07.082 line:80%
Aren't these the sort of questions
they should be asking?

00:31:07.165 --> 00:31:09.918 line:80%
The palace already screened them,
so they had no other choice.

00:31:10.001 --> 00:31:11.002 line:80%
Ah.

00:31:11.753 --> 00:31:15.256 line:80%
I swear, they really need a new PR team.

00:31:15.924 --> 00:31:16.966 line:80%
Tsk, tsk, tsk.

00:31:18.426 --> 00:31:20.345 line:80%
How did you two meet?

00:31:20.428 --> 00:31:21.846 line:80%
Our first meeting?

00:31:23.056 --> 00:31:24.057 line:80%
Mmm…

00:31:27.769 --> 00:31:29.729 line:80%
[chuckles] It was quite a long time ago.

00:31:30.355 --> 00:31:32.148 line:80%
We went to the same school.

00:31:32.232 --> 00:31:34.859 line:80%
Were you just strictly classmates
back then?

00:31:34.943 --> 00:31:36.111 line:80%
No romantic feelings?

00:31:36.945 --> 00:31:39.989 line:80%
And Your Royal Highness?
You are here too, are you not?

00:31:40.073 --> 00:31:41.825 line:80%
Will you receive demerit points as well?

00:31:41.908 --> 00:31:42.951 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:31:44.577 --> 00:31:46.496 line:80%
Sparks flew back then as well.

00:31:47.205 --> 00:31:50.041 line:80%
But nothing ever happened
between us back then.

00:31:50.125 --> 00:31:51.126 line:80%
It just felt like…

00:31:51.960 --> 00:31:53.795 line:80%
we came from two very different worlds.

00:31:53.878 --> 00:31:56.589 line:80%
From when you were
just acquaintances to now,

00:31:56.673 --> 00:31:58.591 line:80%
what would you say is the biggest change?

00:32:02.762 --> 00:32:04.097 line:80%
Hmm…

00:32:06.266 --> 00:32:07.851 line:80%
Being overprotective?

00:32:07.934 --> 00:32:08.935 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:32:11.271 --> 00:32:13.273 line:80%
She will be staying here
for the time being.

00:32:17.152 --> 00:32:18.820 line:80%
I am trying to protect you!

00:32:22.907 --> 00:32:25.243 line:80%
He must think that I'd break
at the lightest touch.

00:32:26.995 --> 00:32:28.121 line:80%
As if I were made of glass.

00:32:31.875 --> 00:32:33.668 line:80%
[both laugh]

00:32:35.211 --> 00:32:36.212 line:80%
"Glass."

00:32:38.298 --> 00:32:40.884 line:80%
Why? Do I seem unbreakable to you?

00:32:43.762 --> 00:32:44.763 line:80%
Just kidding.

00:32:45.346 --> 00:32:46.431 line:80%
[giggles]

00:32:59.861 --> 00:33:00.862 line:80%
[sighs]

00:33:05.533 --> 00:33:07.076 line:80%
[sighs]

00:33:07.160 --> 00:33:08.161 line:80%
[Hyeon] Your Royal Highness.

00:33:08.745 --> 00:33:10.747 line:80%
Why don't you take a break
and look at this?

00:33:10.830 --> 00:33:12.165 line:80%
What is it?

00:33:12.248 --> 00:33:16.127 line:80%
This is the draft
of Ms. Seong's interview.

00:33:20.882 --> 00:33:22.467 line:80%
A CHAT WITH SEONG HUIJU,
CEO OF CASTLE BEAUTY

00:33:22.550 --> 00:33:23.593 line:80%
[I-AN scoffs]

00:33:23.676 --> 00:33:24.761 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:33:36.648 --> 00:33:39.234 line:80%
Steward Kim, Her Ladyship is here!

00:33:44.614 --> 00:33:45.698 line:80%
Goodness me!

00:33:46.324 --> 00:33:47.992 line:80%
Your Ladyship!

00:33:57.252 --> 00:33:59.170 line:80%
You act like it's been years.

00:33:59.254 --> 00:34:00.588 line:80%
I know, right?

00:34:00.672 --> 00:34:03.716 line:80%
At this rate, another lovers' quarrel
will be the death of me.

00:34:03.800 --> 00:34:06.302 line:80%
As if you didn't snatch the <i>hopae</i>
from my hands.

00:34:06.386 --> 00:34:07.303 line:80%
[stammers]

00:34:07.887 --> 00:34:09.222 line:80%
[Youngseon] Why is Ms. Do here?

00:34:10.056 --> 00:34:11.224 line:80%
She's my right-hand woman.

00:34:12.809 --> 00:34:14.269 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:34:14.352 --> 00:34:15.562 line:80%
Let's go inside.

00:34:15.645 --> 00:34:16.646 line:80%
[chuckling] Yes, ma'am.

00:34:19.899 --> 00:34:20.900 line:80%
What?

00:34:21.442 --> 00:34:22.443 line:80%
[sighs]

00:34:23.570 --> 00:34:26.030 line:80%
I asked for those files ages ago and yet…

00:34:27.866 --> 00:34:28.867 line:80%
Wow.

00:34:28.950 --> 00:34:30.368 line:80%
Let me call you back.

00:34:34.664 --> 00:34:35.707 line:80%
Do you like it?

00:34:36.833 --> 00:34:39.878 line:80%
Oh… It's just so pretty.

00:34:40.712 --> 00:34:41.713 line:80%
[door opens]

00:34:44.173 --> 00:34:46.467 line:80%
You can go now.
I'll take care of the rest.

00:34:47.385 --> 00:34:48.845 line:80%
No, it'll only take a second…

00:34:51.890 --> 00:34:54.434 line:80%
Very well. Please let me know
if you need anything.

00:35:02.859 --> 00:35:04.360 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Return to my private residence.</i>

00:35:05.904 --> 00:35:06.905 line:80%
What?

00:35:07.447 --> 00:35:08.489 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:35:08.573 --> 00:35:12.076 line:80%
Am I someone who shows up
and leaves on your command?

00:35:12.160 --> 00:35:13.578 line:80%
We'll start packing immediately.

00:35:14.454 --> 00:35:15.496 line:80%
Ms. Do.

00:35:15.580 --> 00:35:17.290 line:80%
I'm worried about leaving you alone.

00:35:17.373 --> 00:35:19.584 line:80%
At least you'll be safe there
with the Royal Guard.

00:35:20.668 --> 00:35:22.211 line:80%
-Right?
-Of course.

00:35:22.295 --> 00:35:24.547 line:80%
Our Royal Guard is top-notch.

00:35:24.631 --> 00:35:26.132 line:80%
[I-AN] One more thing.

00:35:26.215 --> 00:35:27.967 line:80%
Please go ahead, Your Royal Highness.

00:35:28.051 --> 00:35:29.802 line:80%
There's a spy at my private residence.

00:35:30.470 --> 00:35:31.471 line:80%
A spy?

00:35:32.055 --> 00:35:33.723 line:80%
Is it someone on your staff?

00:35:33.806 --> 00:35:34.682 line:80%
Do you have a name?

00:35:37.477 --> 00:35:38.686 line:80%
Just a moment.

00:35:39.187 --> 00:35:40.813 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:35:43.066 --> 00:35:44.984 line:80%
PERSONAL DETAILS REPORT
LEE AREUM

00:35:45.068 --> 00:35:46.069 line:80%
Oh?

00:35:46.819 --> 00:35:47.904 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:35:47.987 --> 00:35:49.822 line:80%
Any chance of wiretaps or hidden cameras?

00:35:49.906 --> 00:35:50.907 line:80%
That's impossible.

00:35:50.990 --> 00:35:53.618 line:80%
Both the palace and private residence
are checked regularly.

00:35:53.701 --> 00:35:57.163 line:80%
Then that means she only reports
what she can see and hear.

00:35:58.122 --> 00:36:01.417 line:80%
How many times
have I told you to just kick her out?

00:36:01.501 --> 00:36:03.544 line:80%
She'll only be replaced by someone else.

00:36:05.213 --> 00:36:06.547 line:80%
I'll move in with you.

00:36:07.423 --> 00:36:08.424 line:80%
You will?

00:36:08.508 --> 00:36:09.634 line:80%
Yes.

00:36:11.970 --> 00:36:12.971 line:80%
Would that be okay?

00:36:17.308 --> 00:36:18.309 line:80%
As you wish.

00:36:21.270 --> 00:36:22.814 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:36:23.481 --> 00:36:25.316 line:80%
Ms. Do, I need to take this.

00:36:32.657 --> 00:36:33.658 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:36:35.451 --> 00:36:36.452 line:80%
The palace, tomorrow?

00:36:37.662 --> 00:36:39.038 line:80%
We need to plan the wedding.

00:36:40.289 --> 00:36:42.166 line:80%
I'll have a car sent for you.

00:36:43.292 --> 00:36:44.460 line:80%
Don't drive yourself.

00:36:46.629 --> 00:36:47.630 line:80%
[call disconnects]

00:36:47.714 --> 00:36:48.673 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:36:48.756 --> 00:36:49.757 line:80%
[♪ piano music playing]

00:37:07.859 --> 00:37:08.860 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] Huiju.

00:37:10.153 --> 00:37:11.154 line:80%
Jeongwoo!

00:37:13.489 --> 00:37:14.490 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:37:17.035 --> 00:37:19.954 line:80%
But are you going to help us
plan the wedding too?

00:37:20.038 --> 00:37:20.955 line:80%
You didn't think I would?

00:37:21.039 --> 00:37:24.292 line:80%
I'm the prime minister, and your wedding
is basically a state affair.

00:37:25.168 --> 00:37:26.169 line:80%
That's true.

00:37:29.505 --> 00:37:32.216 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness,
Ms. Seong has arrived.

00:37:35.553 --> 00:37:36.554 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:37:38.598 --> 00:37:40.767 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Prime Minister Min
is here as well.

00:37:42.977 --> 00:37:43.978 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:37:44.812 --> 00:37:45.813 line:80%
Show them in.

00:37:48.274 --> 00:37:49.275 line:80%
[sighs]

00:38:04.749 --> 00:38:06.125 line:80%
Did the two of you…

00:38:08.544 --> 00:38:09.754 line:80%
come here together?

00:38:10.421 --> 00:38:11.422 line:80%
No.

00:38:12.381 --> 00:38:13.591 line:80%
We met at the palace gates.

00:38:14.634 --> 00:38:15.635 line:80%
I see.

00:38:18.638 --> 00:38:19.889 line:80%
Now then,

00:38:20.473 --> 00:38:21.474 line:80%
shall we get started?

00:38:26.896 --> 00:38:29.023 line:80%
Can we push back the meeting a bit?

00:38:29.899 --> 00:38:31.484 line:80%
Yeah. Around two hours?

00:38:33.319 --> 00:38:35.279 line:80%
-This is taking longer than expected.
-Ms. Do!

00:38:36.072 --> 00:38:37.073 line:80%
[♪ whimsical music playing]

00:38:37.156 --> 00:38:38.407 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Okay, thank you.

00:38:40.451 --> 00:38:42.245 line:80%
You must be here with Ms. Seong.

00:38:42.328 --> 00:38:43.621 line:80%
-Yes.
-I see.

00:38:44.705 --> 00:38:47.083 line:80%
Did you see the flowers on the way in?

00:38:47.166 --> 00:38:50.211 line:80%
The palace becomes
a flower paradise this time of year.

00:38:50.294 --> 00:38:51.754 line:80%
-Especially…
-Hmm?

00:38:52.797 --> 00:38:54.590 line:80%
-Ms. Do?
-Yes?

00:38:54.674 --> 00:38:58.010 line:80%
The lilies and hydrangeas
are especially magnificent.

00:38:58.094 --> 00:38:59.220 line:80%
If you're free later…

00:38:59.303 --> 00:39:00.471 line:80%
[Lady Choi clearing throat]

00:39:01.097 --> 00:39:02.306 line:80%
Hydrangeas?

00:39:04.350 --> 00:39:05.601 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:39:06.144 --> 00:39:07.145 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:39:07.728 --> 00:39:08.729 line:80%
See you.

00:39:13.693 --> 00:39:17.989 line:80%
Your royal wedding will be held on a scale
comparable to the Crown Prince's.

00:39:18.865 --> 00:39:20.032 line:80%
[I-AN] For what reason?

00:39:20.116 --> 00:39:21.742 line:80%
The royal family has seen many tragedies.

00:39:21.826 --> 00:39:23.744 line:80%
The people suffered just as much.

00:39:23.828 --> 00:39:25.705 line:80%
Thus, we must take this chance

00:39:25.788 --> 00:39:28.875 line:80%
to remind the public that the Crown
still stands strong.

00:39:28.958 --> 00:39:31.127 line:80%
-That will--
-Make the Crown more useful.

00:39:32.211 --> 00:39:34.714 line:80%
Both at home and abroad.

00:39:36.757 --> 00:39:38.259 line:80%
[chuckles] That's right.

00:39:38.342 --> 00:39:40.136 line:80%
There are notable economic benefits too.

00:39:41.679 --> 00:39:45.099 line:80%
Royal weddings generate more revenue
than they cost, after all.

00:39:45.183 --> 00:39:46.434 line:80%
How much does it cost?

00:39:47.268 --> 00:39:48.269 line:80%
Around…

00:39:50.354 --> 00:39:51.564 line:80%
[♪ whimsical music playing]

00:39:51.647 --> 00:39:53.065 line:80%
[coughs] So hot!

00:39:53.149 --> 00:39:54.567 line:80%
Are you okay? Did you burn your tongue?

00:39:55.193 --> 00:39:56.360 line:80%
No, I'm fine.

00:39:58.070 --> 00:39:59.113 line:80%
Wait, hold on.

00:39:59.822 --> 00:40:02.325 line:80%
What kind of revenue
could justify that cost?

00:40:02.950 --> 00:40:04.076 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:40:06.621 --> 00:40:08.831 line:80%
Seong Huiju will soon become my wife.

00:40:09.749 --> 00:40:11.083 line:80%
Please mind your conduct.

00:40:16.672 --> 00:40:17.673 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:40:20.885 --> 00:40:22.720 line:80%
You do not need
to keep up appearances with me.

00:40:23.888 --> 00:40:24.805 line:80%
[Huiju] Oh…

00:40:25.848 --> 00:40:27.475 line:80%
You see… [chuckles]

00:40:29.268 --> 00:40:30.978 line:80%
Jeongwoo knows everything.

00:40:32.772 --> 00:40:33.773 line:80%
[laughs]

00:40:37.693 --> 00:40:38.694 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:40:43.241 --> 00:40:44.242 line:80%
[sighs]

00:40:44.742 --> 00:40:46.869 line:80%
Until your divorce is finalized
without incident…

00:40:50.331 --> 00:40:53.709 line:80%
I will do my best to assist you both.

00:40:58.214 --> 00:40:59.215 line:80%
Yay!

00:41:03.219 --> 00:41:04.262 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:41:07.390 --> 00:41:08.391 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:41:09.058 --> 00:41:11.519 line:80%
Your father seemed pleased, didn't he?

00:41:11.602 --> 00:41:12.561 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:41:12.645 --> 00:41:13.646 line:80%
Of course.

00:41:13.729 --> 00:41:16.524 line:80%
Who would ever be against their in-laws
securing royal ties?

00:41:17.525 --> 00:41:19.235 line:80%
Wait, that's why he was pleased?

00:41:19.318 --> 00:41:21.654 line:80%
Not because I'm going
to inherit Castle Group?

00:41:21.737 --> 00:41:23.698 line:80%
-[car approaching]
-We can't be sure of that just yet.

00:41:24.198 --> 00:41:25.199 line:80%
What?

00:41:25.741 --> 00:41:27.827 line:80%
Wait, what's that supposed to mean?

00:41:27.910 --> 00:41:28.744 line:80%
Han Dayeong.

00:41:31.664 --> 00:41:33.165 line:80%
What's that brat doing here?

00:41:33.666 --> 00:41:35.876 line:80%
-Uh, hello.
-Babe, shoulders back.

00:41:36.752 --> 00:41:37.586 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:41:38.671 --> 00:41:39.839 line:80%
Here to see your parents?

00:41:39.922 --> 00:41:43.592 line:80%
Yeah, my father wanted to give
my sister-in-law a wedding gift.

00:41:44.427 --> 00:41:46.512 line:80%
I assume you saw the news?

00:41:48.264 --> 00:41:50.266 line:80%
I thought you weren't close
to your sister.

00:41:50.933 --> 00:41:52.768 line:80%
-Well, you know, family can be…
-[Dayeong chuckles]

00:41:53.728 --> 00:41:57.148 line:80%
What are you talking about?
They're basically inseparable.

00:41:58.316 --> 00:41:59.442 line:80%
Uh, yes, we're close.

00:42:00.401 --> 00:42:03.654 line:80%
-Really?
-She also leans on me so much.

00:42:04.155 --> 00:42:06.574 line:80%
I'm wondering if I should
join her in the palace.

00:42:06.657 --> 00:42:07.783 line:80%
-You?
-You?

00:42:09.952 --> 00:42:10.995 line:80%
Yeah.

00:42:11.620 --> 00:42:13.873 line:80%
It's not like she has a mother to lean on.

00:42:14.623 --> 00:42:17.209 line:80%
I have to step in. What choice do I have?

00:42:18.878 --> 00:42:20.504 line:80%
She has no other choice…

00:42:21.630 --> 00:42:25.551 line:80%
I swear I had no choice. He walked in
when I was talking to Ms. Do--

00:42:25.634 --> 00:42:27.219 line:80%
You call that an excuse?

00:42:28.304 --> 00:42:30.014 line:80%
That's just what happened.

00:42:32.099 --> 00:42:33.267 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:42:35.686 --> 00:42:36.812 line:80%
[sighs]

00:42:36.896 --> 00:42:38.647 line:80%
But it's not all so bad, is it?

00:42:39.398 --> 00:42:41.567 line:80%
-What?
-We need the approval

00:42:41.650 --> 00:42:44.236 line:80%
of the royal family and the Cabinet
for every little thing.

00:42:44.320 --> 00:42:46.697 line:80%
With Jeongwoo on our side,

00:42:46.781 --> 00:42:49.325 line:80%
we don't need to worry
about the Cabinet anymore.

00:42:49.408 --> 00:42:50.826 line:80%
How are you so sure?

00:42:50.910 --> 00:42:52.661 line:80%
-What?
-About Prime Minister Min.

00:42:53.954 --> 00:42:56.290 line:80%
How can you be sure
he'll always take our side?

00:42:56.374 --> 00:42:57.416 line:80%
Because, obviously…

00:42:57.500 --> 00:42:58.626 line:80%
That's a bit too naïve, no?

00:42:59.251 --> 00:43:00.169 line:80%
Excuse me?

00:43:00.252 --> 00:43:06.592 line:80%
A businesswoman should know better
than to trust people so easily, no?

00:43:11.097 --> 00:43:12.098 line:80%
[sighs]

00:43:13.307 --> 00:43:16.435 line:80%
Your Royal Highness
and I only started getting in sync.

00:43:17.061 --> 00:43:19.897 line:80%
Then it would make more sense
for me to trust him over you, no?

00:43:20.523 --> 00:43:22.817 line:80%
He's always been on my side
since we were kids.

00:43:22.900 --> 00:43:24.860 line:80%
-What?
-Let's face it.

00:43:24.944 --> 00:43:28.030 line:80%
For all I know,
you could just bail out on me again.

00:43:28.823 --> 00:43:30.866 line:80%
Calling you fickle
would be an understatement.

00:43:30.950 --> 00:43:32.118 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:43:32.201 --> 00:43:33.869 line:80%
"Fi… Fickle"?

00:43:33.953 --> 00:43:37.498 line:80%
Just know that
I really want to draw up a contract,

00:43:37.581 --> 00:43:39.166 line:80%
but I'm doing my best to hold back.

00:43:40.543 --> 00:43:42.545 line:80%
[scoffs, laughs]

00:43:44.422 --> 00:43:45.506 line:80%
Draw it up.

00:43:46.590 --> 00:43:47.758 line:80%
-What?
-Draw it up.

00:43:47.842 --> 00:43:49.301 line:80%
-Draw it up?
-Draw it up.

00:43:50.719 --> 00:43:51.887 line:80%
Let's draw it up!

00:44:00.104 --> 00:44:02.189 line:80%
[♪ fiery music playing]

00:44:04.066 --> 00:44:05.609 line:80%
So we will divorce…

00:44:05.693 --> 00:44:06.986 line:80%
Within three years at the latest.

00:44:07.069 --> 00:44:08.988 line:80%
The sooner, the better.

00:44:09.071 --> 00:44:10.072 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:44:10.614 --> 00:44:13.534 line:80%
-Post-divorce asset division?
-Aside from the clothes on your back,

00:44:13.617 --> 00:44:16.662 line:80%
any real estate or assets
bestowed by virtue of royal status

00:44:16.745 --> 00:44:18.038 line:80%
must be relinquished.

00:44:18.122 --> 00:44:19.081 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:44:19.790 --> 00:44:21.000 line:80%
Might as well fight over pennies.

00:44:21.083 --> 00:44:22.418 line:80%
"Pennies"?

00:44:23.878 --> 00:44:25.087 line:80%
Very well, then.

00:44:25.671 --> 00:44:28.716 line:80%
However, I will not be relinquishing
my title or rank.

00:44:28.799 --> 00:44:31.218 line:20%
The privileges attached to them
shall also be maintained.

00:44:31.802 --> 00:44:34.513 line:80%
-For life.
-As long as you do not cause

00:44:34.597 --> 00:44:37.433 line:80%
public controversy or violate the law,
you shall retain them.

00:44:39.226 --> 00:44:40.227 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:44:42.605 --> 00:44:43.772 line:80%
There's more.

00:44:45.191 --> 00:44:46.192 line:80%
One.

00:44:46.775 --> 00:44:47.776 line:80%
[sighs]

00:44:47.860 --> 00:44:50.112 line:80%
All matters concerning the palace
shall remain confidential,

00:44:50.196 --> 00:44:51.655 line:80%
during the marriage and thereafter.

00:44:51.739 --> 00:44:52.740 line:80%
Two.

00:44:53.240 --> 00:44:55.618 line:80%
All matters between us
shall remain confidential,

00:44:55.701 --> 00:44:57.161 line:80%
during the marriage and thereafter.

00:44:57.244 --> 00:44:58.996 line:80%
-Three.
-All matters shall

00:44:59.663 --> 00:45:00.873 line:80%
remain confidential.

00:45:02.875 --> 00:45:04.001 line:80%
I hear you.

00:45:04.919 --> 00:45:07.588 line:80%
-In turn, Your Royal Highness--
-If secrecy proves difficult,

00:45:08.631 --> 00:45:09.757 line:80%
just forget it happened.

00:45:10.299 --> 00:45:11.926 line:80%
[♪ somber music playing]

00:45:12.009 --> 00:45:13.219 line:80%
It's all pretend anyway.

00:45:14.303 --> 00:45:15.346 line:80%
It won't matter.

00:45:25.564 --> 00:45:29.026 line:80%
Your Royal Highness,
the Queen Mother has arrived.

00:45:36.242 --> 00:45:37.576 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness.

00:45:38.327 --> 00:45:39.453 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:42.540 --> 00:45:43.541 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:45:50.089 --> 00:45:51.173 line:80%
Escort her in.

00:46:10.276 --> 00:46:11.318 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:46:11.819 --> 00:46:13.237 line:80%
I am Huiju of the Seong Family.

00:46:16.240 --> 00:46:17.241 line:80%
[door closes]

00:46:19.493 --> 00:46:21.870 line:80%
I stopped by
after hearing you were both here.

00:46:21.954 --> 00:46:24.832 line:80%
I wanted to ask
if you two would join me for dinner.

00:46:25.666 --> 00:46:28.961 line:80%
We are soon to be family, after all.

00:46:34.091 --> 00:46:35.092 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:46:41.473 --> 00:46:43.601 line:80%
-Enjoy.
-You too.

00:46:51.650 --> 00:46:54.486 line:80%
Will Ms. Seong be okay?
What if she gets indigestion?

00:46:54.570 --> 00:46:56.739 line:80%
She'll be fine. She has an iron stomach.

00:46:56.822 --> 00:46:58.157 line:80%
No, you see…

00:46:58.240 --> 00:46:59.658 line:80%
The Queen Mother can be…

00:47:00.951 --> 00:47:03.078 line:80%
a bit old-school.
She can be super intense.

00:47:03.162 --> 00:47:04.705 line:80%
It's fine.

00:47:04.788 --> 00:47:06.707 line:80%
Ms. Seong is quite the rebel too.

00:47:07.875 --> 00:47:08.876 line:80%
I see.

00:47:08.959 --> 00:47:11.211 line:80%
So stop worrying and eat already.

00:47:11.295 --> 00:47:13.922 line:80%
Our bosses will be on edge
after their dinner.

00:47:16.050 --> 00:47:17.176 line:80%
All right then.

00:47:17.760 --> 00:47:21.472 line:80%
Truth be told, I was worried
they might really fall for one another.

00:47:21.555 --> 00:47:25.476 line:80%
I mean, come on.
Who wouldn't fall for Our Royal Highness?

00:47:25.559 --> 00:47:27.478 line:80%
With that face and figure,
and those shoulders like…

00:47:27.561 --> 00:47:28.562 line:80%
Nothing to worry about.

00:47:28.646 --> 00:47:30.648 line:80%
Ms. Seong likes trophy men.

00:47:31.690 --> 00:47:32.691 line:80%
What did you say?

00:47:32.775 --> 00:47:33.817 line:80%
Trophy men.

00:47:33.901 --> 00:47:36.070 line:80%
Ones that show up and leave on command.

00:47:36.153 --> 00:47:37.279 line:80%
Spineless men.

00:47:38.072 --> 00:47:39.907 line:80%
So just eat your food.

00:47:39.990 --> 00:47:42.660 line:80%
The chances of a man
who's summoned people his whole life

00:47:42.743 --> 00:47:45.579 line:80%
and a woman
who's bossed people around her whole life

00:47:45.663 --> 00:47:48.290 line:80%
falling for each other are basically nil.

00:47:53.462 --> 00:47:55.047 line:80%
-What about you, Ms. Hyejeong?
-What?

00:47:59.009 --> 00:48:01.428 line:80%
What's your type?

00:48:01.512 --> 00:48:02.513 line:80%
[♪ soft piano music playing]

00:48:08.727 --> 00:48:09.728 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:48:12.022 --> 00:48:13.023 line:80%
[Hyeon clears throat]

00:48:13.899 --> 00:48:17.069 line:80%
They really know how to cook
their wild greens here.

00:48:17.152 --> 00:48:18.320 line:80%
Kudos, Auntie.

00:48:42.010 --> 00:48:44.596 line:80%
I do hope the food is to your taste.

00:48:45.973 --> 00:48:48.058 line:80%
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:48:51.645 --> 00:48:53.063 line:80%
This liquor is made from pears.

00:48:54.815 --> 00:48:56.275 line:80%
It is quite strong.

00:48:56.358 --> 00:48:57.651 line:80%
Ah.

00:48:57.735 --> 00:48:58.652 line:80%
Queen Mother.

00:48:59.611 --> 00:49:00.612 line:80%
She…

00:49:01.280 --> 00:49:02.781 line:80%
Can you not handle your alcohol?

00:49:03.365 --> 00:49:05.784 line:80%
I certainly can.

00:49:05.868 --> 00:49:06.869 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:49:13.834 --> 00:49:15.294 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:49:21.550 --> 00:49:23.051 line:80%
[Huiju, Yun chuckling]

00:49:24.887 --> 00:49:26.638 line:80%
Wait, were you really scolded that much?

00:49:28.724 --> 00:49:31.351 line:80%
He wrote letters of apology so frequently.

00:49:31.435 --> 00:49:33.645 line:80%
I am sure there were enough
to make a whole book.

00:49:34.229 --> 00:49:35.564 line:80%
Is that so?

00:49:35.647 --> 00:49:38.108 line:80%
I guess you were quite the troublemaker.

00:49:39.401 --> 00:49:40.444 line:80%
Drink some water.

00:49:40.527 --> 00:49:42.738 line:80%
Hold on. You're blushing.

00:49:42.821 --> 00:49:44.364 line:80%
You're totally blushing.

00:49:44.948 --> 00:49:46.658 line:80%
[gasps] Your face is red.

00:49:48.786 --> 00:49:51.371 line:80%
If His Majesty, your father,
had still been with us…

00:49:55.501 --> 00:49:58.462 line:80%
I wonder what he would have said
about this union.

00:50:00.631 --> 00:50:02.382 line:80%
[♪ emotional piano music playing]

00:50:06.220 --> 00:50:07.221 line:80%
Queen Mother.

00:50:12.935 --> 00:50:14.311 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:50:16.939 --> 00:50:19.441 line:80%
He would have requested
a letter of apology.

00:50:20.567 --> 00:50:23.987 line:80%
He so frequently scolded you
for standing in your brother's way.

00:50:24.530 --> 00:50:28.700 line:80%
Surely, he would not have approved
of you standing in your nephew's way.

00:50:29.701 --> 00:50:30.869 line:80%
You should stop there.

00:50:37.125 --> 00:50:39.169 line:80%
Can you truly claim to be wholly innocent

00:50:40.462 --> 00:50:42.965 line:80%
in the death of the late King?

00:50:48.095 --> 00:50:50.681 line:80%
What goes through your mind
when you look at His Majesty?

00:50:51.890 --> 00:50:53.433 line:80%
Do you wish to stand in his way

00:50:53.976 --> 00:50:56.687 line:80%
and eliminate him,
just as you did the late King?

00:51:12.077 --> 00:51:13.120 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:51:23.380 --> 00:51:25.007 line:80%
Do you know why he was given

00:51:26.425 --> 00:51:28.302 line:80%
the royal title of "I-AN"?

00:51:32.264 --> 00:51:33.724 line:80%
"I" as in "rule."

00:51:34.308 --> 00:51:35.601 line:80%
"AN" as in "peace."

00:51:37.019 --> 00:51:38.770 line:80%
It calls upon him to refrain

00:51:40.480 --> 00:51:42.399 line:80%
from harming the stability of the Crown.

00:52:01.627 --> 00:52:04.046 line:80%
Please excuse us now.

00:52:13.388 --> 00:52:17.142 line:80%
It will soon be time
to close the palace gates.

00:52:17.768 --> 00:52:18.769 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:26.151 --> 00:52:27.277 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:52:31.281 --> 00:52:32.366 line:80%
Slow down.

00:52:35.911 --> 00:52:37.245 line:80%
I said, slow down.

00:52:39.373 --> 00:52:42.584 line:80%
Just know I'm holding back
because we're not married yet.

00:52:43.168 --> 00:52:44.836 line:80%
You keep saying you're holding back.

00:52:44.920 --> 00:52:48.006 line:80%
If I had it my way,
the Queen Mother would be pulverized--

00:52:48.090 --> 00:52:49.091 line:80%
Whoa!

00:52:51.009 --> 00:52:52.010 line:80%
[sighs]

00:52:58.308 --> 00:52:59.393 line:80%
Just hang in there.

00:53:00.727 --> 00:53:02.187 line:80%
As soon as we're married,

00:53:02.270 --> 00:53:06.274 line:80%
I will clear everything
that stands in your way.

00:53:07.192 --> 00:53:08.610 line:80%
[♪ soft piano music playing]

00:53:14.825 --> 00:53:15.826 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:53:18.537 --> 00:53:19.830 line:80%
You don't believe me?

00:53:22.082 --> 00:53:23.083 line:80%
I do.

00:53:24.501 --> 00:53:27.337 line:80%
So get me out of here.

00:53:28.338 --> 00:53:29.339 line:80%
What?

00:53:31.466 --> 00:53:33.135 line:80%
I don't want to sleep here tonight.

00:54:02.956 --> 00:54:04.374 line:80%
Should you be driving right now?

00:54:05.584 --> 00:54:07.586 line:80%
Leaving the palace was defiance in itself.

00:54:09.421 --> 00:54:10.589 line:80%
Aren't you scared?

00:54:12.007 --> 00:54:13.717 line:80%
The accident wasn't too long ago.

00:54:16.344 --> 00:54:17.429 line:80%
I like driving.

00:54:26.104 --> 00:54:27.230 line:80%
It feels like flying.

00:54:28.231 --> 00:54:29.232 line:80%
And I can go fast.

00:54:32.402 --> 00:54:34.654 line:80%
I'm not allowed to run or ride a bike.

00:54:35.280 --> 00:54:36.573 line:80%
But I'm allowed to drive.

00:54:38.200 --> 00:54:39.618 line:80%
I don't understand the logic.

00:54:45.082 --> 00:54:46.333 line:80%
[♪ emotional music continues]

00:54:46.416 --> 00:54:47.417 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:56.718 --> 00:54:58.470 line:80%
Do you want to fly for real?

00:55:12.234 --> 00:55:13.568 line:80%
[♪ music crescendos]

00:55:17.656 --> 00:55:18.657 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:55:23.411 --> 00:55:24.996 line:80%
Do you intend to propose to me?

00:55:26.289 --> 00:55:28.625 line:80%
You've watched way too many dramas.

00:55:28.708 --> 00:55:30.210 line:80%
Then why are we here?

00:55:30.836 --> 00:55:31.962 line:80%
Did you rent this?

00:55:32.045 --> 00:55:33.088 line:80%
It's mine.

00:55:35.966 --> 00:55:39.553 line:80%
So what? You want me to fly here?

00:55:40.345 --> 00:55:42.013 line:80%
You obviously can't fly here.

00:55:42.097 --> 00:55:45.934 line:80%
We can fly right over there.

00:55:46.977 --> 00:55:47.978 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:55:48.061 --> 00:55:49.020 line:80%
Wait here.

00:55:56.695 --> 00:55:57.696 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:56:02.492 --> 00:56:04.703 line:80%
You should not run, Your Majesty!

00:56:04.786 --> 00:56:05.996 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:56:06.079 --> 00:56:07.122 line:80%
[pants]

00:56:07.205 --> 00:56:08.206 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:56:10.041 --> 00:56:12.294 line:80%
I dried these myself, Ms. Do.

00:56:13.295 --> 00:56:14.296 line:80%
[slurps]

00:56:14.379 --> 00:56:15.672 line:80%
How is it?

00:56:15.755 --> 00:56:17.257 line:80%
-It's nice.
-I knew it!

00:56:17.340 --> 00:56:19.301 line:80%
I don't offer this to just anyone.

00:56:19.384 --> 00:56:20.385 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:56:21.136 --> 00:56:22.470 line:80%
But I had some yesterday.

00:56:23.471 --> 00:56:24.890 line:80%
-Don't you have work to do?
-Mmm.

00:56:27.642 --> 00:56:28.602 line:80%
Uncle!

00:56:28.685 --> 00:56:30.228 line:80%
-Your Majesty.
-Oh, Your Majesty.

00:56:32.814 --> 00:56:34.774 line:80%
Oh, uh, is it just you here?

00:56:35.358 --> 00:56:36.484 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:56:36.568 --> 00:56:37.652 line:80%
Where is Uncle?

00:56:37.736 --> 00:56:41.198 line:80%
I heard Ms. Seong was here as well.

00:56:41.281 --> 00:56:43.909 line:80%
Oh, we are also wondering
where they could be--

00:56:43.992 --> 00:56:45.410 line:80%
You can just tell me, Your Majesty.

00:56:45.493 --> 00:56:47.537 line:80%
I will be sure to pass along any message.

00:56:48.663 --> 00:56:49.998 line:80%
No need.

00:56:51.416 --> 00:56:52.542 line:80%
[sighs]

00:56:52.626 --> 00:56:54.628 line:80%
-Your Majesty.
-A mighty sigh from His Majesty…

00:56:54.711 --> 00:56:56.213 line:80%
Your Majesty, what is the matter?

00:56:57.047 --> 00:56:58.089 line:80%
He's so cute.

00:57:11.895 --> 00:57:12.979 line:80%
Is someone chasing you?

00:57:13.563 --> 00:57:14.648 line:80%
Why is no one here?

00:57:15.190 --> 00:57:16.983 line:80%
I asked them to clear out.

00:57:17.567 --> 00:57:18.610 line:80%
Can I get you anything?

00:57:20.362 --> 00:57:22.697 line:80%
"A royal can only eat
in verified restaurants."

00:57:24.532 --> 00:57:25.951 line:80%
Wh-- What are you doing?

00:57:26.034 --> 00:57:27.869 line:80%
Just do whatever you want today.

00:57:29.120 --> 00:57:30.997 line:80%
-What?
-I told you it's just us here.

00:57:32.207 --> 00:57:35.460 line:80%
-But a royal--
-Royals never marry commoners.

00:57:35.543 --> 00:57:36.753 line:80%
So why are you marrying me?

00:57:47.222 --> 00:57:49.140 line:80%
[♪ sprightly piano music playing]

00:58:01.653 --> 00:58:02.654 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:58:03.613 --> 00:58:04.614 line:80%
[I-AN exhales loudly]

00:58:07.951 --> 00:58:09.452 line:80%
My goodness.

00:58:10.578 --> 00:58:11.788 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:58:12.289 --> 00:58:15.125 line:80%
-Who gets seasick on a yacht?
-It's just indigestion.

00:58:15.709 --> 00:58:16.710 line:80%
It's indigestion.

00:58:19.045 --> 00:58:20.046 line:80%
[laughing]

00:58:20.130 --> 00:58:21.131 line:80%
[coughs]

00:58:23.800 --> 00:58:25.844 line:80%
I mean, I could prick your finger for you.

00:58:26.469 --> 00:58:28.680 line:80%
-What?
-There should be a needle somewhere.

00:58:29.889 --> 00:58:31.808 line:80%
-A royal…
-Are you scared?

00:58:31.891 --> 00:58:35.312 line:80%
Because a prick would hurt so much?
Shaking in your boots?

00:58:35.395 --> 00:58:36.938 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:58:37.939 --> 00:58:39.941 line:80%
Fine. Let's do it.

00:58:45.030 --> 00:58:47.449 line:80%
Are you sure this works?
Not just a placebo effect?

00:58:48.992 --> 00:58:50.035 line:80%
Ouch!

00:58:50.702 --> 00:58:51.870 line:80%
[sighs]

00:58:55.248 --> 00:58:56.499 line:80%
I feel all better now.

00:58:56.583 --> 00:58:57.500 line:80%
Ouch!

00:58:59.669 --> 00:59:02.005 line:80%
How did I ever put my trust
in such a cowardly prince?

00:59:02.088 --> 00:59:03.882 line:80%
[scoffs] "Cowardly"?

00:59:03.965 --> 00:59:04.966 line:80%
I am…

00:59:06.217 --> 00:59:08.553 line:80%
just not familiar with home remedies.

00:59:08.636 --> 00:59:09.679 line:80%
Let's go now.

00:59:11.181 --> 00:59:12.349 line:80%
Go on.

00:59:12.432 --> 00:59:14.559 line:80%
I told you I'd let you experience flying.

00:59:16.353 --> 00:59:17.354 line:80%
-Come on.
-Wha--

00:59:31.868 --> 00:59:32.911 line:80%
[inhales deeply]

00:59:34.871 --> 00:59:35.872 line:80%
[giggles]

00:59:37.290 --> 00:59:38.291 line:80%
[I-AN] Oh!

00:59:40.293 --> 00:59:41.294 line:80%
[gasps]

00:59:41.378 --> 00:59:43.713 line:80%
This is too dangerous. Come down now.

00:59:43.797 --> 00:59:44.798 line:80%
Here.

00:59:45.298 --> 00:59:46.383 line:80%
Hold me tight.

00:59:50.178 --> 00:59:51.388 line:80%
[♪ romantic music playing]

00:59:53.556 --> 00:59:54.724 line:80%
[both chuckle]

01:00:00.814 --> 01:00:01.815 line:80%
[sighs]

01:00:10.782 --> 01:00:11.783 line:80%
[laughs]

01:00:12.742 --> 01:00:13.743 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:00:16.121 --> 01:00:18.123 line:80%
[♪ pop ballad playing]

01:01:07.839 --> 01:01:09.174 line:80%
You said you'd let me fly.

01:01:09.799 --> 01:01:11.217 line:80%
Why are you the one flying?

01:01:12.969 --> 01:01:14.929 line:80%
Let's switch. I can hold you.

01:01:15.597 --> 01:01:17.682 line:80%
-Forget it.
-Why not? Come on…

01:01:17.765 --> 01:01:19.684 line:80%
-[yelps]
-[grunts]

01:01:19.767 --> 01:01:21.144 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

01:01:21.227 --> 01:01:22.479 line:80%
[gasps]

01:01:24.731 --> 01:01:25.732 line:80%
[sighs]

01:01:26.649 --> 01:01:27.650 line:80%
[sighs]

01:01:30.778 --> 01:01:32.739 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[gasps]

01:01:41.915 --> 01:01:42.916 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

01:01:43.416 --> 01:01:45.293 line:80%
Are you hurt anywhere?

01:01:51.716 --> 01:01:53.384 line:80%
You said I can do whatever I want.

01:01:57.263 --> 01:01:59.057 line:80%
[♪ romantic music playing]

01:02:06.523 --> 01:02:07.732 line:80%
[♪ soft piano playing]

01:02:36.594 --> 01:02:37.804 line:80%
[♪ orchestral strings playing]

01:03:12.547 --> 01:03:15.425 line:20%
EPILOGUE

01:03:15.508 --> 01:03:16.926 line:20%
[sighs]

01:03:17.010 --> 01:03:18.886 line:20%
You'll be attending
the second half, right?

01:03:21.180 --> 01:03:22.390 line:20%
Probably.

01:03:24.017 --> 01:03:25.518 line:20%
I assume you can waltz?

01:03:25.602 --> 01:03:26.644 line:20%
[chuckles]

01:03:27.478 --> 01:03:28.479 line:20%
Can you?

01:03:29.105 --> 01:03:30.440 line:20%
[scoffs, chuckles]

01:03:32.358 --> 01:03:34.777 line:20%
[♪ piano flourish plays]

01:03:34.861 --> 01:03:37.322 line:20%
I am a top laureate through and through.

01:03:41.242 --> 01:03:44.078 line:80%
[♪ piano flourish plays]

01:03:57.342 --> 01:03:59.010 line:20%
[♪ piano waltz music playing]

01:04:03.848 --> 01:04:04.974 line:20%
[laughing]

01:04:11.314 --> 01:04:12.440 line:20%
[chuckles]

01:04:18.404 --> 01:04:19.572 line:20%
-[exclaims]
-[laughs]

01:04:20.239 --> 01:04:21.282 line:20%
Let's not do that.

01:04:22.700 --> 01:04:23.868 line:20%
Hold me up like this.

01:04:23.951 --> 01:04:25.161 line:20%
Here I come.

01:04:32.877 --> 01:04:33.961 line:20%
[chuckles]

01:04:37.090 --> 01:04:40.009 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:04:42.303 --> 01:04:43.805 line:80%
[♪ upbeat pop song playing]

01:05:18.423 --> 01:05:20.299 line:80%
<i>We were just caught up in the moment.</i>

01:05:20.383 --> 01:05:22.885 line:80%
I mean, it's not like
I threw myself at him.

01:05:22.969 --> 01:05:24.971 line:80%
[groans] Why did I do that?

01:05:25.054 --> 01:05:26.013 line:80%
<i>Not for me.</i>

01:05:26.097 --> 01:05:28.641 line:80%
<i>I didn't do it just because</i>
<i>I was caught up in the moment.</i>

01:05:29.308 --> 01:05:31.060 line:80%
I did it because it's you.

01:05:32.186 --> 01:05:34.981 line:20%
[Hyejeong] <i>Don't you think it's excessive?</i>
<i>Maybe they're falling for each other.</i>

01:05:35.064 --> 01:05:38.401 line:20%
<i>I mean, they actually look like</i>
<i>they just started dating.</i>

01:05:39.152 --> 01:05:41.571 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>Something bothering you?</i>
<i>You've been acting strange.</i>

01:05:41.654 --> 01:05:43.948 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>You're being</i>
<i>unnecessarily sweet to me.</i>

01:05:45.032 --> 01:05:46.242 line:20%
I shall wait.

01:05:46.325 --> 01:05:49.036 line:20%
[Yun] <i>Until the day</i>
<i>you can no longer restrain yourself.</i>

01:05:49.620 --> 01:05:51.706 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>Restraint always followed desire.</i>

01:05:51.789 --> 01:05:53.249 line:20%
<i>But it's not easy this time.</i>

01:05:53.332 --> 01:05:56.294 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>By chance,</i>
<i>do you have feelings for me?</i>

01:05:57.628 --> 01:05:59.630 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:06:10.933 --> 01:06:14.645 line:20%
PERFECT CROWN